movie_title: Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows
title: Entertaining enough
review: It's a Sherlock Holmes movie and is exactly what you'd expect. The only thing I find strange is, what the hell is the point of Naomi Rapace' character? She's just this tertiary character in every scene for no effing reason whatsoever. No dialogue. Just the same dumb look on her face throughout the movie.
